      "content": "i'm tired of everyone telling me that things will get better or that i should \"reach out\" for help. it feels like everyone is just lying to make themselves feel less uncomfortable with how much everything sucks. i dont want the happy version. i want the truth. why does everything feel so meaningless? is it just me or is there actually nothing there?",
